Yes, there is a web series directly based on the notorious movie piracy website called Tamilrockers. The series is titled "Tamil Rockerz" and it premiered on the Indian streaming platform SonyLIV on August 19, 2022.

Here's what you should know about the "Tamil Rockerz" series:

Platform: SonyLIV
Release Date: August 19, 2022
Language: Tamil (also available in Hindi, Telugu, Malayalam, Kannada, Bengali, and Marathi)
Genre: Thriller, Crime, Drama, Action
Director: Arivazhagan Venkatachalam
Cast: Arun Vijay, Vani Bhojan, Ishwarya Menon, and others.
Plot: The series revolves around the activities of the Tamilrockers website, which has been a significant threat to the Tamil film industry by leaking newly released movies online. It follows a police officer's (played by Arun Vijay) efforts to track down the people behind the piracy network.
Number of Episodes: 8 (in the first season)
